                <div type="edition" xml:lang="okz-Latn" rendition="class:83231 maturity:00000">
<p>
   <lb n="1"/><gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/>duttaraṣacchataśakaparigraha ta gi dvādaśī ket śrāvaṇa Uttarāṣādhanakṣatra
   <lb n="2"/><gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/>divasavāra gi sre ta tel ti kurāk śūragrāma tve Ai cdiṅ vrīdāṅ
   <lb n="3"/><supplied reason="lost">Aṁvi</supplied> tnal mratāñ bhā prasanna loḥ karoṁ tnal mratāñ
   <lb n="4"/><gap reason="lost" quantity="6" unit="character"/> kapālaśeṣa sre man poñ bhā viśārada jāhv ta kloñ tep
   <lb n="5"/><gap reason="lost" quantity="8" unit="character"/> tel poñ vrau kros Oy ta vraḥ kamratāṅ Añ
   <lb n="6"/>śrīśaṅka<supplied reason="lost">ranā</supplied>rāyaṇa
</p>
                 
